    <section id="Bloodhound+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>Bloodhound Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
         project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class="graduated">The Bloodhound project graduated on 2013-03-20</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>Bloodhound is a software development collaboration tool, including issue tracking, wiki and repository browsing.</p>
    </section>
